		<h2 class="article-ttl">
			Listen to the bugs, and eat them too - Bugs Summer Night Festival Report.
		</h2>
	</a>
	
																														<div class="tag-btn"><a href="http://bioclub.org/en/tags/news">#NEWS</a></div>
		
							<div class="thumb">
				<a href="http://bioclub.org/en/project-report/bugsnouryo-sai-report" class="ct-block hv-op">
					<span class="img-wrapper"><img src="http://bioclub.org/assets/images/bugreport.png" alt="Listen to the bugs, and eat them too - Bugs Summer Night Festival Report."></span>
					
																<p class="ct-link-lead">Bugs are actors who perform the role of seasons. They affect our emotions in various ways. At the end of the summer, BioClub hosted an event to enjoy the cool summer nights associated with these bugs. The event is called Listen to the bugs, and eat them too - Bugs Summer Night Festival.</p>
